name: Great White Shaldorn
description:
(From the DARK series)

Ordered by the Emperor, Nurtured by the Elder, and bathed in the blood of the Empress, the "Great White Shaldorn" was given birth by the Scientians. 

What once slept in an unbreakable cocoon was now unleashed on the lands beyond, a beast of might, tasked to obliterate the living.
